text: Jonas Hunziker (born 15 May 1994) is a Swiss freestyle skier who competes internationally. He competed in the 2011, 2013 and 2015 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and represented Switzerland at the 2018 Winter Olympics in PyeongChang, where he made the slopestyle final. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Switzerland Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
